      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BROWNLOW (7) has missed the frame at his last couple of starts but just a few runs back broke the clock when winning over 350m at Q Straight, taking a Grade 5 in a head turning 18.88. Can measure up on top win three back. COMICAL WARREN (2) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.3 lengths away in second (25.75) behind Don't Cry Mama at this track. Will give a great sight again. QUEST FOR PACE (4) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 5th and beaten 8 lengths at this track (26.24). Should be about the mark. WISE KEVIN (3) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
